 Day Zero is the atmosphere. The sounds of the jungle blend harmoniously with the throbbing basslines that resonate through day and night.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.webp 380w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.webp 620w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.jpg 380w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.jpg 620w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Day Zero Tulum\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://edm.com/.image/t_share/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.jpg\" data-src=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNDA0NTY1NDQ0NjY2ODg5/dzt2025_0112_032841-2611_alivecoverage.jpg\" height=\"1365\" width=\"2048\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ec/o Alive Coverage\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s no coincidence that the event is rooted in the spiritual calendar of the Mayans, who saw endings not as finalities but as fertile ground for new beginnings.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eAirrica and Cole Knight delivered the energy that the moment called for with a hypnotic b2b set, their melodic grooves intertwining with the meditative hum of the jungle. Sainte Vie, one of Mexico’s brightest talents, delivered a live performance that embraced a fusion of organic and electronic elements woven together like past and present.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThen came the kind of moment that defines the Day Zero experience. Solomun, Michael Bibi and Lazarus took to the stage for an epic b3b set that was daring and seamless. Previously, their creative fusion only existed in the hearts and minds of their respective fans, but those lucky enough to attend their set witnessed an event that will be remembered for years to come.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.webp 380w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.webp 620w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.jpg 380w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.jpg 620w, https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Damian Lazarus, Michael Bibi, Solomon\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://edm.com/.image/t_share/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.jpg\" data-src=\"https://edm.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNDA0MzgzMTc2OTkyMjY1/dzt2025_0112_110829-8537_drb.jpg\" height=\"1365\" width=\"2048\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ec/o Alive Coverage\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eDay Zero is often described as a party, but that description alone feels inadequate. Under the glow of art installations inspired by Mayan mythology and amidst the flickering light of fire dancers, the festival’s deeper purpose becomes clear as not only is it a place to escape reality but an opportunity to face it with a newfound sense of wonder.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can find out more about Day Zero \u003ca href=\"https://dayzerofestival.com/locations/tulum/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"follow-day-zero\"\u003eFOLLOW DAY ZERO:\u003c/h2\u0